.netrc

# ---- Editor / tooling ----
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*~

# ---- Project scratch ----
# Quick Look / icon rasterization scratch is generated under /tmp, not tracked.
# Generated app icons in Assets/ (*.icns, *-1024.png) are derived from the SVG
# masters; keep the SVGs tracked. Uncomment the next lines to stop tracking the
# generated raster output:
# Assets/*.icns
# Assets/*-1024.png

# ---- Distribution / local build output ----
# The assembled .app links Homebrew's libtorrent/openssl at absolute paths, so
# it's a local build artifact — rebuild it with `swift build -c release`.
/dist/

# ---- Local scratch binaries (one-off Sendable/audit probes) ----
/check_sendable
/check_sendable_strict
